Man Group plc. is a world-leading alternative investment management business. It has expertise in a wide range of liquid investment styles including managed futures, equity, credit and convertibles, emerging markets, global macro and multi-manager, combined with powerful product structuring, distribution… MoreMan Group plc. is a world-leading alternative investment management business. It has expertise in a wide range of liquid investment styles including managed futures, equity, credit and convertibles, emerging markets, global macro and multi-manager, combined with powerful product structuring, distribution and client service capabilities.
The Information Technology department at Man Group plc. builds IT services and platforms across the enterprise, while collaborating closely with the business. The company maintains a data center which is located in London. 

The IT department is classified by several… MoreThe Information Technology department at Man Group plc. builds IT services and platforms across the enterprise, while collaborating closely with the business. The company maintains a data center which is located in London. 

The IT department is classified by several smaller units specializing in different forms of IT. These units include security, enterprise architecture, business continuity, IT infrastructure, eCommerce operations, voice/data communications, eCommerce delivery, and software development. 

The company's project management and project methodology is based on Agile. In the beginning of 2011, Man Group signed a 10-year Turnkey data center lease agreement with Digital Realty for an enterprise disaster recovery location.





