nts  Is a Supplemental   Form 8 (Open Positions) attached?    YES/NO    Date of disclosure:  13th July   2017  Contact name:  Matthew Irwin  Telephone number:  02071447255  Public disclosures under Rule 8 of the Code must be made to a Regulatory Information Service and must also be emailed to the Takeover Panel at monitoring@disclosure.org.uk.  The Panel's Market Surveillance Unit is available for consultation in relation to the Code's disclosure requirements on +44 (0)20 7638 0129. The Code can be viewed on the Panel's website at www.thetakeoverpanel.org.uk. 


